<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٨٣٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/13865">‌يُونُسُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>، <a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٣٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6962">‌يَحْيَى بْنِ عُبَيْدٍ الْبَهْرَانِيِّ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">‌ابْنَ عَبَّاسٍ </a>،<span class="c5"> يَقُولُ:</span> <span class="c2">«نَهَى رَسُولُ اللهِ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ عَنِ الْحَنْتَمِ وَالدُّبَّاءِ وَالنَّقِيرِ وَالْمُزَفَّتِ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>